title: Strangejuice - Sparrow (New Indie Album Late 2013)
description:
Description
Strangejuice is one of the most innovative and talented songwriters and producers to come out of Australia in many years.

Released September 2013

This album is an ecclectic collection of songs recorded by Strangejuice between 2011 - 2013, including the popular singles Calling Luci, Sugar Lane, Carpsosina Distincta, Hinden Bird, and Marigolds.
